---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms of Use | ShopifyCalc" description="Terms of use for ShopifyCalc — disclaimer of rate accuracy, carrier trademarks, and site usage.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-8"><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By using ShopifyCalc (<strong>shopify-fee-calc.com</strong>), you agree to these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, please discontinue use of the site immediately.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">2. No Affiliation with Shopify Inc.</h2>
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-300 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">
          <p class="font-medium text-yellow-900">Important Disclaimer</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-yellow-800">ShopifyCalc is an <strong>independent, third-party website</strong>. We are not affiliated with, sponsored by, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected to Shopify Inc. "Shopify" and the Shopify logo are registered trademarks of Shopify Inc. Use of the Shopify name on this site is for descriptive/nominative purposes only to identify the platform our tools are designed to help users with.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">3. Shipping Rate Disclaimer — IMPORTANT</h2>
        <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-300 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">
          <p class="font-medium text-red-900">Rates Are Estimates Only</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-red-800">All shipping rates displayed on this website are <strong>approximate estimates for informational purposes only</strong>. They are derived from publicly available carrier rate schedules and may not reflect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1 text-red-800">
            <li>Current published rates (carriers update rates periodically, often annually)</li>
            <li>Fuel surcharges, residential delivery fees, address correction fees, or other accessorial charges</li>
            <li>Negotiated/contract rates (which may be significantly lower for high-volume shippers)</li>
            <li>Dimensional weight adjustments for oversized packages</li>
            <li>Holiday or peak season surcharges</li>
            <li>Rates specific to your account type (retail vs. commercial)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2 text-red-800 font-medium">Always verify rates directly with carriers before committing to shipping costs. ShopifyCalc is not responsible for any financial decisions made based on rates displayed on this site.</p>
        </div>
        <p>For official current rates, visit:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>USPS: <a href="https://www.usps.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">usps.com</a></li>
          <li>UPS: <a href="https://www.ups.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">ups.com</a></li>
          <li>FedEx: <a href="https://www.fedex.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">fedex.com</a></li>
          <li>DHL: <a href="https://www.dhl.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">dhl.com</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">4. Third-Party Trademarks</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">All carrier names, logos, and trademarks mentioned on this website are the property of their respective owners and are used for informational/nominative reference purposes only:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>USPS</strong> (United States Postal Service) is a federal agency of the US government.</li>
          <li><strong>UPS</strong> and the UPS logo are registered trademarks of United Parcel Service of America, Inc.</li>
          <li><strong>FedEx</strong> and the FedEx logo are registered trademarks of Federal Express Corporation.</li>
          <li><strong>DHL</strong> and the DHL logo are registered trademarks of Deutsche Post AG.</li>
          <li><strong>Shopify</strong> and the Shopify logo are registered trademarks of Shopify Inc.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">ShopifyCalc is not affiliated with, sponsored by, or endorsed by any of the above companies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">5. Informational Purposes Only</h2>
        <p>All calculators, rate comparisons, and content on this website are provided for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. Nothing on this site constitutes financial, legal, or business advice. You should consult with qualified professionals before making business decisions.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>ShopifyCalc, its owners, operators, and contributors are not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or special damages arising from:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Reliance on rate estimates displayed on this site</li>
          <li>Errors or inaccuracies in calculator results</li>
          <li>Business decisions made based on information on this site</li>
          <li>Interruptions in site availability</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>The website design, code, original written content, and data compilations on this site are the intellectual property of ShopifyCalc. Carrier rate data is derived from publicly available sources and is presented in a transformed/comparative format under fair use principles.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">8. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the United States. Any disputes shall be resolved in the appropriate courts of the United States.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:legal@shopify-fee-calc.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">legal@shopify-fee-calc.com</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
